Author: Alex Clark
Author-email: aclark@aclark.net
License: UNKNOWN
Description: django-pci-auth
        ===============
        
        .. Warning::
        
            This application validates passwords via **un-encrypted AJAX** communication. Please **use with SSL only**!
        
